snippet.title: Clock Tower II: the Struggle Within (PS1) Intro Movie
snippet.description: The trailer movie to Clock Tower II: the Struggle Within, aka Clock Tower Ghosthead (Human Entertainment, 1998).  Like the first two Clock Tower games, Ghosthead is a point-and-click suspense horror.
